				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "As the player explore the surrounding of Moonrise, they can encounter a cat playing with a dead tadpole. Upon interacting with this cat, player can learn where the tadpoles are actually being stored at (SWA) or the location of a nearby tunnel they can use in cat form (Non-SWA). Steelclaw is a murdering psychopath who revels in blood and gore."
